text: Kim Wyman (born July 15, 1962) is an American politician. She is the 15th and current Secretary of State of Washington, having won in the 2012 and 2016 state elections. Between 2012 and 2016, she was the only Republican elected to statewide office on the West Coast. In March 2017, Wyman was diagnosed with an early form of colon cancer. ==References== ==Other websites== * Campaign website * * Kim Wyman at Project Vote Smart * * * Profile from Thurston County Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Long Beach, California Category:Politicians from Washington (state) Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
